  "title": "[Entry Level] Campaign Marketing Trainee",
  "description": "<p><em><strong>Campaign Marketing Trainee (Entry Level – Fast-Track Growth)</strong></em></p><p>Ascend Marketing Solutions is looking for motivated, ambitious individuals to join as Campaign Marketing Trainees. This entry-level role offers hands-on experience with premium brands, running live marketing campaigns, and learning the ins and outs of sales, event marketing, and brand activation. With performance-based progression and mentorship from industry experts, your growth depends on your effort and results.</p><p>You’ll engage directly with clients, support high-impact campaigns, and gain practical skills that set the foundation for a fast-moving career in marketing and sales. This role is perfect for confident communicators, self-starters, and those eager to learn in a dynamic, results-driven environment.</p>",
